labels.profile:
Noncommercial label from releasing any kind of information in physical and digital format.
Its conception reflects an idea of informational freedom and limitlessness of art (in particular).
Label started in autumn 2010, spontapeously raised after re-release of Genetic Trance 2005 album in digital format.
